            <lg xml:id="TK4">
<l>vēṇṭutal vēṇṭāmai yilāṉaṭi cērntārk</l>
<l>kiyāṇṭu miṭumpai yila</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who meditate the feet of Him who is void of desire or aversion, evil shall never come.</l>
            </lg>
